1993;;Bank Robber;;American;;Nick Mead;;Patrick Dempsey, Lisa Bonet, Judge Reinhold;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_Robber_(film);;Billy (Dempsey), is a well dressed bank robber who decides to do one last heist so he can sail off to a tropical island with his girlfriend, Selina (d'Abo). On his last robbery, he forgets to destroy a surveillance camera. He then must hide out in the Heartbreak Hotel until he can get out of trouble.